title: RISSOLES
directions: Put parsley into mixer bowl, chop for 3 sec/speed 9/MC on.
Add onion to mixer bowl, chop for 2 sec/speed 6/MC on.
Add zucchini or carrot to mixer bowl, chop for 3 sec/speed 5/MC on.
Add remaining ingredients (except dukkah) and pulse turbo for 1 sec/3 times to roughly combine.
Shape into patties and coat in dukkah mixture. Lightly fry or grill until cooked through.
ingredients: 200 g | 7 oz zucchini or carrot, roughly chopped
2 tbsp psyllium husk or almond meal
50 g | 1.8 oz Coconut Garlic Dukkah to crumb or almond meal
